Positive Examples.explanation: One sentence says dancing on the stage while the other sentence says dance performance on the dais, which are clearly giving teh same meaning and are realted to each other. So the classification is entailment.

Positive Examples.explanation: First one says the crowd is cherring at dance performance whereas the second one says enjoying eating the food, there is no relation at all as it is not even contradicting. So it is neutral.

Negative Examples.explanation: One sentence says two dogs are fighting and the other says two dogs are sharing which is a contradiction but classified as entailment. So this is a wrong example.
